title: [Yegharren Plain, Grasslands]
description: The trail winds downward to the east as the ground slopes gently into another wide plain of grassland below.  A sea of dark, rustling grass higher than a halfling's head leads off as far as the eye can see to the north and west.

The trail winds downward to the east as the ground slopes gently into another wide plain of grassland below.  A sea of green and golden grass higher than a halfling's head leads off as far as the eye can see to the north and west.
